{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your loyal dog has been taken by a monstrous evil, and it's time to make him pay.<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203110/extras/samurai-gif-2-ezgif.com-optimize.gif?t=1737640423\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><i>Rogue Inferno</i></strong> is a grid-based roguelike deckbuilder where strategy and positioning are the keys to victory.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Grid-Based Combat</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Every move matters. Position yourself strategically on the grid to dodge attacks, outmaneuver enemies, and unleash devastating combos.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203110/extras/1-description.png?t=1737640423\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Deck-Building Meets Strategy</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Craft a deck that suits your playstyle! Draw, play, and manage cards each turn to attack, defend, or unleash powerful combos.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203110/extras/cards-closup.png?t=1737640423\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">A Unique Card Upgrade System</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each card comes with a unique mission. Complete its challenge to unlock powerful upgrades and evolve your deck as you play.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203110/extras/reward-closup.png?t=1737640423\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Dozens of Monsters</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Face a wide array of enemies, each with unique behaviors and strategies. From slimes that divide to explosive enemies and mutant tribes, every encounter is a new adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">And Much More!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstat